# Configuration file for the "Folk Hero" background

# Personality Trait				bg[0] 
I judge people by their actions, not their words.::If someone is in trouble, I'm always ready to lend help.::When I set my mind to something, I follow through no matter what gets in my way.::  I have a strong sense of fair play and always try to find the most equitable solution to arguments.::I'm confident in my own abilities and do what I can to instill confidence in others.::Thinking is for other people. I prefer action.::I misuse long words in an attempt to sounds smarter.::I get bored easily. When am I going to get on with my destinty?

# Ideals						bg[1]
Respect: People deserve to be treated with dignity and respect. (Good)::Fairness: No one should get preferential treatment before the law, and no one is above the law. (Lawful)::Freedom: Tyrants must not be allowed to oppress the people. (Chaotic)::Might: If I become strong, I can take what I want- what I deserve. (Evil)::Sincerity: There's no good in pretending to be something I'm not. (Neutral)::Destiny: Nothing and no one can steer me away from my higher calling. (Any)

# Bonds							bg[2]
I have a family, but I have no idea where they are. One day, I hope to see them again.::I worked the land, I loved the land, and I will protect the land.::A proud noble once gave me a horrible beating, and I will take my revenge on any bully I encounter.::My tools are symbols of my past life, and I carry them so that I will never forget my roots.::I protect those who cannot protect themselves.::I wish my childhood sweatheart had some with me to pursue my destiny.

# Flaws							bg[3]
The tyrant who rules my land will stop at nothing to see me killed.::I'm concinced of my significance of my destiny, and blind to my shortcomings and the risk of failure.::The people who knew me when I was young know my shameful secret, so I can never go home again.::I have a weakness for the vices of the city, especialy hard drink.::Secretly, I believe that things would be better if I was a tyrant lording over the land.::I have trouble trusting in my allies.

# Specialty 					bg[4]
I stood up to a tyrant's agents.::I saved people during a natural disaster.::I stood alone against a terrible monster.::I stole from a corrupt merchant to help the poor.::I led a militia to fight off an invading army.::I broke into a tyrant's castle and stole weapons to arm the people.::I trained the peasantry to use farm implements as weapons againsr a tyrant's soldiers.::A lord rescinded an unpopular decree after I led a symbolic act to protect against it.::A celestrial, fey, or similar creature gave me a blessing or revealed my secreat origin.::Recruited into a lord's army, I rose to leadership and was commended for my heroism. 

# Feature						bg[5]
Rustic Hospitality: Since you come from the ranks of the common folk, you fit in among them wit ease. You can find a place to hide, rest, or recuperate among other commoners, unless you have shown yourself to be a danger to them. They will shield you from the law or anyone else searching for you, though they will not risk their lives for you.
